== usage ==
# `git clone git://github.com/uhyo/jinrou.git`
# `cd jinrou`
# `npm install`
# Build front scripts
## `cd front`
## `npm install`
## `npm run production-build`
## `cd ..`
# run mongodb
# run redis
# SS_ENV=production SS_PACK=1 node app.js

== development ==
To run in development mode, just run `node app.js`.

Also, to keep updating the front-end assets, run `npm run watch` in the `front` directory.

